    <ul>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/active_hash_relation">active_hash_relation</a></h3>
        <p>Simple gem that allows you to run multiple ActiveRecord::Relation using hash. Perfect for APIs.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/activeadmin-logins">Activeadmin::Logins</a></h3>
        <p>Tracks user logins and displays results in Active Admin (<a href="/blog/2015/05/activeadmin-logins/">post</a>).</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/middleman-boilerplate">middleman-boilerplate</a></h3>
        <p>Our boilerplate for Middleman 4 projects.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/rubycas-server-activerecord">Rubycas::Server::Activerecord</a></h3>
        <p>ActiveRecord adapter for RubyCAS Server Core (RubyCAS2.0).</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/kong-tictail-theme">Kong Tictail Theme</a></h3>
