      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/kollegorna/apsis-ruby">APSIS API wrapper for Ruby</a></h3>
        <p>A simple API wrapper for the APSIS mail marketing service. Currently only supports adding subscribers to a mailing list.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="https://github.com/persand/blaskan">Blaskan</a></h3>
